        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Thank you for this clarification. I missed this subtle difference.\n\nFor a bit of context, I am a maintainer of the [nixvim](https://github.com/nix-community/nixvim) project and we are planning our transition to the new internal `vim.lsp` API and dropping internal `require(\"lspconfig\")` usage.\nI never used these specific `bitbake` language servers and am thus not familiar with them. Nonetheless, I should have checked the config files more carefully.\n\n\n> We would appreciate your help in answering this question and updating the configs. We need actual users to maintain the configs they are interested in, since there are 1000s of configs.\n\nSure! Thanks for all the tremendous work you do in neovim by the way.\nI opened https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/pull/4109. Hope it helps :)",
